    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>  .video-gallery-first, .video-gallery-rest {    display: grid;    gap: 10px;    margin: 25px 0;  }    /* 桌面端布局 */  .video-gallery-first {    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);  }  .video-gallery-rest {    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);  }    /* 平板端布局 */  @media (max-width: 900px) {    .video-gallery-rest {      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);    }  }    /* 移动端布局 - 强制保持2+3布局 */  @media (max-width: 600px) {    .video-gallery-first {      grid-template-columns: 1fr;    }    .video-gallery-rest {      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);    }    /* 确保第三行视频单独一行 */    .video-gallery-rest iframe:nth-child(3) {      grid-column: 1 / -1;    }  }    /* 超小屏幕优化 */  @media (max-width: 400px) {    .video-gallery-first, .video-gallery-rest {      gap: 8px;    }  }  .video-item {    position: relative;    width: 100%;    padding-bottom: 56.25%;    height: 0;    overflow: hidden;    border-radius: 6px;    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);    background: #000;  }  .video-item iframe {    position: absolute;    top: 0; left: 0;    width: 100%; height: 100%;    border: none;  }</style><div class="hero-banner" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #4a6491 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; margin: 0 0 30px; color: white; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">    <h1 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">欢迎加入RC机器人协会！</h1>    <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 20px; opacity: 0.9;">这里是机器人爱好者的乐园，更是你通往技术巅峰的起点站！</p>    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 50px; padding: 15px 30px; display: inline-block;">      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">各位同学大家好！欢迎来到福建理工大学学生RC机器人协会！</p>    </div>  </div></div><div class="section-title" style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 25px;">  <h2 style="display: inline-block; margin: 0; padding: 0 20px; position: relative;">    <span style="background: white; position: relative; z-index: 2; padding: 0 15px;">双赛道国家级赛事平台</span>    <div style="position: absolute; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #d9534f, #5bc0de); width: 100%; top: 50%; left: 0; transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 1;"></div>  </h2>  <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #6c757d;">我们协会分为两大核心部门，分别负责：</p></div><div class="competition-cards" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">  <a href="https://www.robomaster.com/zh-CN" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; flex: 1; min-width: 300px; max-width: 450px;">    <div class="card" style="border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div class="card-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9534f 0%, #c12e2a 100%); padding: 20px; color: white;">        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">          <div style="font-size: 2rem;"></div>          <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">RoboMaster机甲大师赛</h3>        </div>      </div>      <div class="card-body" style="padding: 25px; background: white;">        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0;">全国对抗性机器人赛事</p>        <p style="color: #6c757d;">无论你钟情于激烈的红蓝对抗...</p>        <div style="margin-top: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px;">          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">            <span style="background: #d9534f; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">!</span>            战术对抗 · 团队作战 · 实时竞技          </p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="https://www.cnrobocon.net/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; flex: 1; min-width: 300px; max-width: 450px;">    <div class="card" style="border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div class="card-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5bc0de 0%, #2a96b5 100%); padding: 20px; color: white;">        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">          <div style="font-size: 2rem;"></div>          <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">RoboCon亚太机器人大赛</h3>        </div>      </div>      <div class="card-body" style="padding: 25px; background: white;">        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0;">创意任务型机器人挑战</p>        <p style="color: #6c757d;">还是偏爱创意的机械协作...</p>        <div style="margin-top: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px;">          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">            <span style="background: #5bc0de; color: white; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">!</span>            创新设计 · 任务解决 · 技术融合          </p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a></div><div class="video-gallery-first">  <div><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114617980291815&bvid=BV1SW78zFEnq&cid=30297427491&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>  <div><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=115117975019394&bvid=BV1jhhizoErD&cid=32054838033&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div></div><div class="video-gallery-rest">  <iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114971912445859&bvid=BV1CgtVzcE9Y&cid=31489592502&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>  <iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114525906933503&bvid=BV1NQJTz8EsZ&cid=30015818557&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>  <iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=1253425276&bvid=BV1VJ4m1H7Ft&cid=1514037188&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><div class="section-title" style="text-align: center; margin: 50px 0 30px;">  <h2 style="display: inline-block; margin: 0; padding: 0 20px; position: relative;">    <span style="background: white; position: relative; z-index: 2; padding: 0 15px;">六大组别开放招募</span>    <div style="position: absolute; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #5cb85c, #f0ad4e, #d9534f); width: 100%; top: 50%; left: 0; transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 1;"></div>  </h2>  <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #6c757d;">选择你感兴趣的领域，开启机器人技术之旅</p></div><div class="team-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; margin-bottom: 50px;">  <a href="/groups/mechanical" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5cb85c 0%, #449d44 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">⚙️</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">机械组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">从CAD建模到实体搭建，亲手打造钢铁之躯！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #5cb85c;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #5cb85c; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：SolidWorks · 机械设计 · 3D打印</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="/groups/electronic-control" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0ad4e 0%, #ec971f 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🔌</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">电控组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">玩转电路板与代码，赋予机器人灵魂与动力！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #f0ad4e;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #f0ad4e; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：STM32 · C/C++ · 嵌入式开发</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="/groups/hardware" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9534f 0%, #c9302c 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🔋</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">硬件组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">硬件选型、焊接调试，构建稳定的电子神经系统！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #d9534f;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #d9534f; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：PCB设计 · 电路调试 · 焊接技术</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="/groups/vision" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5bc0de 0%, #2aabd2 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">👁️</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">视觉组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">机器视觉算法研发，让机器人拥有"火眼金睛"！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #5bc0de;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #5bc0de; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：OpenCV · 深度学习 · 图像处理</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="/groups/media" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #337ab7 0%, #2a5d8a 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">📸</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">宣传组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">用镜头和文字记录团队成长，打造协会高光时刻！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #337ab7;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #337ab7; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：摄影剪辑 · 新媒体运营 · 内容创作</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a>  <a href="/groups/operations" class="team-card-link" style="text-decoration: none;">    <div class="team-card" style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.3s; cursor: pointer;">      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e44ad 0%, #732d91 100%); padding: 18px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">        <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">📊</div>        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem;">运营组</h3>      </div>      <div style="padding: 22px;">        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">赛事统筹、资源管理，保障战队高效运转！</p>        <div style="margin-top: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #8e44ad;">          <p style="margin: 0; color: #8e44ad; font-size: 0.95rem;">掌握技能：项目管理 · 资源协调 · 活动策划</p>        </div>      </div>    </div>  </a></div><div class="training-section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; margin: 40px 0; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">    <div style="display: inline-flex; background: #5bc0de; color: white; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 50px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">      <div style="font-size: 1.5rem;"></div>      <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">零基础？别担心！</h3>    </div>    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6;">      无论你是零基础小白还是有一定基础的同学，我们都有经验丰富的学长学姐手把手带教——从基础工具使用到复杂系统设计，从小组实战项目到全国赛场历练，助你逐步成长为独当一面的技术大牛！    </p>    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 25px;">      <div style="background: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">        <p style="margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;"><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 阶梯式培训体系</p>      </div>      <div style="background: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">        <p style="margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;"><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 竞赛项目驱动</p>      </div>      <div style="background: white; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">        <p style="margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;"><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 手把手教学制度</p>      </div>    </div>  </div></div><div class="cta-section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%); color: white; padding: 50px 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 50px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">  <div style="position: absolute; top: -50px; right: -50px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%;"></div>  <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -30px; left: -30px; width: 150px; height: 150px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%;"></div>    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">在这里，你不仅能收获硬核的工程技能</h2>    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">      更能结识志同道合的伙伴，共同经历机器人从图纸到赛场的蜕变过程！每一次调试的坚持、每一次胜利的欢呼，都将成为你大学生活中最难忘的回忆！    </p>    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin-top: 20px;">      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 15px;">        招新进行中！立即加入开启你的机器人征程      </p>    </div>  </div></div>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
